title: Jayhawks drubbed by No. 3 Baylor 66-7
text:
Home › AP Sports › Jayhawks drubbed by No. 3 Baylor 66-7 Jayhawks drubbed by No. 3 Baylor 66-7 Baylor tight end LaQuan McGowan gets past Kansas safety Michael Glatczak to score a touchdown on Saturday in Lawrence.
